        <definition>uint32_t raytrace::BottomAccelerationStructureBuildInfo::compactedSizeOutputBufferOffsetInBytes</definition>
        <argsstring></argsstring>
        <name>compactedSizeOutputBufferOffsetInBytes</name>
        <qualifiedname>raytrace::BottomAccelerationStructureBuildInfo::compactedSizeOutputBufferOffsetInBytes</qualifiedname>
        <initializer>= 0</initializer>
        <briefdescription>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Ignored when compactedSizeOutputBuffer is nullptr. compactedSizeOutputBuffer has to be large enough to store a uint64_t at that offset. Offset has to be 64 bit aligned. </para>
